                     THE SEVEN CHAKRAS AND ASSOCIATED ASPECTS

         -----------------------------------------------------------------
                   By, Damon Pike (AstralWizard@cup.portal.com)
               From Astral Pathways -- Guidance to spiritual growth
         -----------------------------------------------------------------

            Chakras  are energy centers in the body that are  associated
       with  a  variety  states  of  evolution,  consciousness,  organs,
       glands,  colors,  light,  and  stones/crystals.  There are  seven
       chakras in the human body.

       1st Chakra (Root) Muladhara
       ---------------------------
              Relates to: Anus, Rectum, Colon, Adrenals.

       Colors Associated: Black, Red

         Stones/Crystals: Black Tourmaline     Bloodstone
                          Obsidian             Realgar
                          Blue Onyx            Rhodonite
                          Smokey Quartz        Garnet

             Energy Info: Ground spirit forces. Ability to work lovingly
                          on the physical plane.

       2nd Chakra (Sexual) Svadhisthana
       --------------------------------
              Relates to:  Pelvic  cavity/area,  Reproductive  system,
                           Ovaries, Prostate, Testicles.

       Colors Associated: Red, Orange

         Stones/Crystals: Ruby            Citrine
                          Wulfenite       Amber
                          Carnelian

            Energy  Info: Creative forces utilized into all aspects of
                          being. High soul procreation. Direction.



                                      Page 1




       3rd Chakra (Solar Plexus) Manipura
       ----------------------------------
              Relates to: Abdominal  area,  Spleen,  Navel,  Digestive
                          system.

       Colors Associated: Orange, Yellow

         Stones/Crystals: Citrine         Sulphur
                          Topaz           Calcite
                          Apatite

             Energy Info: Assimilation  of   experience.   Digestion.
                          Positive use of personal power. Manifest
                          goals.

       4th Chakra (Heart) Anahata
       --------------------------
              Relates to: Thoracic cavity,  Heart,  Rib  cage,  Lungs,
                          Thymus.

       Colors Associated: Green, Pink

         Stones/Crystals: Adventurine          Rhodochrocite
                          Peridot              Rose Quartz
                          Malachite            Kunzite
                          Emerald              Morganite
                          Dioptase             Pink Tourmaline
                          Green Tourmaline

             Energy Info: Release emotionally suppressed trauma. Soul/
                          Heart consciousness. Expressing love and
                          emotion.

       5th Chakra (Throat) Vishuddha
       -----------------------------
              Relates to: Throat, Voice, Neck, Thyroid, Para-thyroid.

       Colors Associated: Blue

         Stones/Crystals: Blue LaceAgate       Turquoise
                          Amazonite            Gem Silica
                          Celestite            Aquamarine
                          Chrysocholla

             Energy Info: Ability to verbalize. Self expression.

       6th Chakra (Third Eye/Psychic Center) Ajna
       ------------------------------------------
              Relates to: Third eye, Higher brain centers, Pituitary.

       Colors Associated: Indigo, Violet

         Stones/Crystals: Sodalite             Flourite
                          Azurite              Sugelite
                          Lapis                Amethyst
                          Sapphire

             Energy Info: Indigo- Clearing subconscious to channel
                          intuition. Purple- Balanced state of mind.
                          Psychic abilites.

                                      Page 2




       7th Chakra (Crown) Sahasrata
       ----------------------------
              Relates to: Crown, Highest brain centers, Pineal.

       Colors Associated: Gold, White, Purple.

         Stones/Crystals: Heloidor             Clear Quartz
                          Gold Topaz           Diamond
                          Selenite

             Energy Info: Personal identification with infinite. Oneness
                          with  Universe.   Peace.   Wisdom.   Spiritual
                          center.

